{"tid":737641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"背心女搵男友驚揭情人已婚　激動危坐簷篷","createTime":"2018-07-11T03:43:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-11T07:51:38.000Z","uid":54373,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2b96452b55891a53e1a7753d51886a09fe293e5f","tid":737641,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T03:43:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180711/photo/bkn-20180711071445500-0711_00822_001_01b.jpg?20180711113122\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180711%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180711071445500-0711_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20180711113122&h=a93d15ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180711/photo/bkn-20180711071445500-0711_00822_001_04b.jpg?20180711113122\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180711%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180711071445500-0711_00822_001_04b.jpg%3F20180711113122&h=411eee97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n馬鞍山耀安邨耀欣樓，今早(11日)6時35分，一名20餘歲身穿黑色吊帶背心女子，登門到上址一單位尋找男友，據現場消息稱，當時男方妻子應門，女子始驚悉男友原來瞞着她已婚，登時情緒激動，攀出18樓走廊欄河危坐外牆簷篷，人妻大驚，立即報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n警方到場展開游說，消防亦張開救生氣墊戒備，惟女子充耳不聞，更不時玩手機，又用紙巾抹眼淚，大批街坊在場圍觀，在對峙逾2個小時後，尋死女子始接受勸喻返回安全地方，但拒絕送院檢驗。<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線：<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222<br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000<br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288<br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000<br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281<br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350"},{"pid":"c9d690f3467f8bbe15ede064ccaa7bd195908799","tid":737641,"uid":8867,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T03:43:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5de552979f6bec64fdcc60ee5d5b4f51807f86be","tid":737641,"uid":12285,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c9d690f3467f8bbe15ede064ccaa7bd195908799","tid":737641,"uid":8867,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T03:43:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T03:44:37.000Z","msg":"垃圾"